<!-- AI PERFORMANCE SECTION -->
<section class="gpu-section">
  <div class="eyebrow">// advanced ai ecosystem</div>
  <h2 class="section-h">AI-Powered <span style="color:var(--gold)">Legal Intelligence</span></h2>
  <p class="section-sub">LexAI runs on The most advanced legal AI available — fast, accurate, and built specifically for legal professionals.</p>
  <div class="gpu-grid">
    <div class="gpu-card">
      <div class="gpu-icon">⚡</div>
      <div class="gpu-t">AI Parallel Processing</div>
      <div class="gpu-d">Analyze 200-page contracts in 4.2 seconds. AI runs thousands of legal inference operations simultaneously — CPU-based tools take minutes.</div>
      <div class="gpu-stat">4.2s avg contract analysis</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gpu-card">
      <div class="gpu-icon">🧠</div>
      <div class="gpu-t">Transformer Inference at Scale</div>
      <div class="gpu-d">Advanced AI models process entire case files in a single pass — analyzing clauses, risks, and precedents simultaneously.</div>
      <div class="gpu-stat">Opus 4 • Sonnet 4 • Haiku</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gpu-card">
      <div class="gpu-icon">🔬</div>
      <div class="gpu-t">Real-Time OCR + Document Vision</div>
      <div class="gpu-d">Upload photos of physical legal documents, scanned PDFs, or handwritten notes. AI-powered OCR extracts and analyzes text in seconds.</div>
      <div class="gpu-stat">AI vision • image-to-text</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gpu-card">
      <div class="gpu-icon">🌐</div>
      <div class="gpu-t">Internet-Powered Research</div>
      <div class="gpu-d">Live web search integrated into every research query. LexAI finds the most recent statutes, regulations, and court decisions — not just training data.</div>
      <div class="gpu-stat">Live web + case law databases</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gpu-card">
      <div class="gpu-icon">📊</div>
      <div class="gpu-t">Embedding-Based Case Matching</div>
      <div class="gpu-d">Vector embeddings find analogous cases across 4M+ opinions in milliseconds. Semantic similarity, not just keyword matching.</div>
      <div class="gpu-stat">Vector search • semantic matching</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gpu-card">
      <div class="gpu-icon">🔄</div>
      <div class="gpu-t">Self-Learning via Fine-Tuning</div>
      <div class="gpu-d">Every correction you make is used to fine-tune preference models. Your LexAI gets exponentially smarter with each interaction — proprietary to LexAI.</div>
      <div class="gpu-stat">Unique • no competitor does this</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

