      <div class="user-d">All 16 AI features at $300/mo. Replace a paralegal. Draft, research, predict — without the overhead.</div>
      <a href="/login" class="user-link">Start solo →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="user-card">
      <div class="user-icon">🏛️</div>
      <div class="user-t">Law Firms</div>
      <div class="user-d">Team and Enterprise plans with shared vaults, agent deployment, white-label reports, and audit trails.</div>
      <a href="/login" class="user-link">Enroll firm →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="user-card">
      <div class="user-icon">🎓</div>
      <div class="user-t">Law Students</div>
      <div class="user-d">Full LexAI Academy with bar exam prep, case simulations, and mooting practice. Bermuda, UK, Canadian, and Caribbean bar tracks.</div>
      <a href="/login" class="user-link">Start learning →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="user-card">
      <div class="user-icon">🏢</div>
      <div class="user-t">Businesses</div>
      <div class="user-d">Contract analysis, compliance checks, immigration document assist, and incorporation — without hiring outside counsel for every question.</div>
      <a href="/login" class="user-link">Get started →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="section" id="features">
  <div class="eyebrow">// full feature set</div>
  <h2 class="section-h">Elite legal AI.<br><span style="color:var(--gold)">Uncompromising quality.</span></h2>
  <p class="section-sub">16 AI features covering every stage of legal work — from first draft to courtroom prediction. All AI-powered. All self-learning.</p>
  <div class="feat-grid">
    <div class="feat"><div class="feat-n">01</div><div class="feat-t">AI Document Drafting</div><div class="feat-d">20+ templates. NDAs, contracts, operating agreements, TOS — jurisdiction-specific, complete, download-ready.</div></div>
    <div class="feat"><div class="feat-n">02</div><div class="feat-t">Contract Analysis</div><div class="feat-d">Upload any contract. Full clause analysis, risk score (0–100), favorable party detection, missing clause flags.</div></div>
    <div class="feat"><div class="feat-n">03</div><div class="feat-t">Case Law Search<span class="feat-badge badge-new">Free Westlaw Alt</span></div><div class="feat-d">Search 4M+ real court opinions via CourtListener + Harvard CAP. Real cases, real citations.</div></div>
    <div class="feat"><div class="feat-n">04</div><div class="feat-t">Internet-Powered Research<span class="feat-badge badge-new">AI</span></div><div class="feat-d">Live web search + database lookup. Find the most recent statutes, regulations, and judgments in real time.</div></div>
    <div class="feat"><div class="feat-n">05</div><div class="feat-t">Litigation Prediction<span class="feat-badge badge-pro">Pro</span></div><div class="feat-d">AI predicts case outcomes. Win probability, settlement likelihood, strategy recommendations.</div></div>
