  <p class="section-sub">No other AI legal platform learns from your corrections — LexAI does — and it's powered by AI fine-tuning, not just prompting.</p>
  <div class="learning-grid">
    <div class="learn-card"><div class="learn-icon">🧠</div><div class="learn-t">Pattern Learning</div><div class="learn-d">Every correction trains LexAI on your preferred clause language, jurisdiction-specific standards, and firm style guides.</div><ul class="learn-steps"><li>Rate any AI output 1–5 stars</li><li>Provide corrections when needed</li><li>AI extracts the preference pattern</li><li>Future outputs apply your style</li></ul></div>
    <div class="learn-card"><div class="learn-icon">📚</div><div class="learn-t">Document Memory</div><div class="learn-d">Every document you upload teaches LexAI about your clients, matters, and practice area. Your institutional knowledge becomes AI-accessible.</div><ul class="learn-steps"><li>Upload any document to Vault</li><li>AI extracts key facts and terms</li><li>Knowledge used in future drafts</li><li>Grows smarter with each document</li></ul></div>
    <div class="learn-card"><div class="learn-icon">⚖️</div><div class="learn-t">Long-Horizon Agents</div><div class="learn-d">LexAI agents perform multi-step self-review. Each step checks the previous for legal accuracy before proceeding.</div><ul class="learn-steps"><li>Multi-step workflows with self-review</li><li>Agents catch their own errors</li><li>Escalates when uncertain</li><li>Full audit trail per step</li></ul></div>
    <div class="learn-card"><div class="learn-icon">📈</div><div class="learn-t">Learning Dashboard</div><div class="learn-d">Track how smart your LexAI has become. Patterns learned, knowledge items stored, personalization level: New → Expert.</div><ul class="learn-steps"><li>Patterns learned counter</li><li>Personalization level tracker</li><li>Average output quality score</li><li>Knowledge base size</li></ul></div>
  </div>
</section>

